The paper deals with the analysis of a new smart gateway diversity architecture for satellite networks, which involves the computation and approximation of the system outage probability. This topic is related to several areas of computer science, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), communication (cs.COMM), systems and control (cs.SY), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
